returns.description:
The REST resource name of the parent from which to retrieve the notification channel descriptors. The expected syntax is:

projects/[PROJECT_ID]

Note that this names the parent container in which to look for the descriptors; to retrieve a single descriptor by name, use the Google::Monitoring::V3::NotificationChannelService::GetNotificationChannelDescriptor operation, instead.
